nks nae!  Has ye looked in tha&#39; pantry?!  There be nothin in there but empty sacks, a few pieces o stale jerky and cobwebs.  Least ye cin duz is head off ta tha store and buy supplies fer yer shindig!  Now gits and bring back real food, nae jest snacks.  We gots plenty o ale and whiskery, so no need ta buys more o either.&#34; <BR> <BR>Diamond begins shooing Storm out of their delves much like she had the badger earlier.  &#34;Nae comes back witout enough food ta feeds tha clan, an hurry they&#39;ll be here in a few hours.&#34; <!-/Text-!> <P> 
